&lt;li&gt;Monitor resident sharps and valuables, ensuring proper labeling, handling, and reporting of safety concerns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate documentation and consistent communication with clinical, billing, and utilization review teams.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Qualifications&lt;/h3&gt;
