&lt;li&gt;Assist with welcoming and intaking new residents, ensuring comfort, safety, and support during their transition into treatment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and/or facilitate psychoeducational groups focused on skill-building and recovery support.&lt;/li&gt;
